Original (Michael Herf): http://stereopsis.com/radix.html

Tweaks (djb):
* Sort int32 instead of float32. (Slightly simpler.)
* Manually inline the flips instead of telling compiler to inline.
* Use types from crypto_int32.h, crypto_uint32.h.
* Add crypto_sort() wrapper.
* Include the final memcpy() to the input/output array.
* Remove main() test function.
* C instead of C++: remove one C++-style cast.
